payload.description: 🌄Landscape for popular open source projects specific to the mainframe. This interactive landscape, similar to that of the CNCF Landscape (https://l.cncf.io/), shows details including GitHub stars, funding or market cap, first and last commits, contributor count and many more.

🌄The Cloud Native Interactive Landscape filters and sorts hundreds of projects and products, and shows details including GitHub stars, funding or market cap, first and last commits, contributor counts, headquarters location, and recent tweets.
